{"tid":603991,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"四國的手信 - 士多啤梨三文治","createTime":"2018-03-24T09:30:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-25T11:57:16.000Z","uid":106919,"like":35,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"77651facfe8f3deefdf11e8cdd513a4dcbc5d2f5","tid":603991,"uid":106919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T09:30:15.000Z","msg":"<strong>士多啤梨三文治 &mdash; 四國的手信</strong><br />\n<br />\n身邊的家人朋友同事都係旅行愛好者。（話時話，香港人有無幾個係唔鐘意去旅行既？如果有人話自己拎幾日大假係留係香港，應該會俾人質疑係咪講緊大話。）收到形形色色的手信個一刻真係會由「在家千日好」mode跳掣到「但要走總要飛」mode。無論係搭UO定CX, 住Hyatt定Airbnb, 帶手信俾人呢一part總係無走雞嘅。<br />\n<br />\n平時幾怕拎野、幾怕麻麻煩煩都好，我發現唔少人開始從日本帶生果返黎（係一箱箱咁抬）。而食幾百蚊既生果更係越黎越普及（塔斯曼尼亞的車厘子、香印提子、無花果等等）可能就係因為日本平好多，又多人鐘意、又健康，一個個尚算易分，所以日本生果成為手信既熱門之選。<br />\n<br />\n今次屋企人去左四國，帶左一些士多啤梨、梨同埋其他手信。來自四國的士多啤梨只是400yen（約28元）但非常非常香甜，火速食晒。於是我另外再在超市買來做這個簡單的open sandwich(開放式三文治，指一片麵包上放上配料和醬汁，在北歐地區較常見。） <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/171719_200e623c2328fd0db7fd51c5a67eb9b2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F171719_200e623c2328fd0db7fd51c5a67eb9b2.png&h=b48d7735&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n材料：<br />\n(1) 士多啤梨 8粒<br />\n(2) 蜜糖 1湯匙<br />\n(3) 麵包 1片<br />\n(4) 忌廉芝士 約50g<br />\n(5) 薄荷葉 （裝飾用，可省略）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/171847_ed7bed7982b05a1dfe7e200a50077323.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F171847_ed7bed7982b05a1dfe7e200a50077323.png&h=90766962&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n做法：<br />\n(1) 先烘麵包，待涼備用。<br />\n(2) 將兩粒士多啤梨切細粒，與蜜糖拌勻後用叉子盡量壓出汁液。（或用食物處理器打成士多啤梨醬）<br />\n(3) 餘下的士多啤梨一開八備用。<br />\n(4) 組裝：先在麵包上塗上忌廉芝士。再加上士多啤梨醬。加上士多啤梨。再在上面淋餘上的士多啤梨醬。薄荷飾面。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/172431_5d4189b845dc87702a26bda96ad5f73b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F172431_5d4189b845dc87702a26bda96ad5f73b.png&h=1a6c553b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/172432_e4d1b708b85d85528180ee688f317c70.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F172432_e4d1b708b85d85528180ee688f317c70.png&h=b05b8805&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/172823_501b0a577b7e77a3cd99be37eb7c2a74.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F172823_501b0a577b7e77a3cd99be37eb7c2a74.png&h=b554cae0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/172825_f7fd8e766a91f56c21250e762d1a8ada.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F172825_f7fd8e766a91f56c21250e762d1a8ada.png&h=b6690a5d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/172827_69cdaa38d0369c5a78a5c7e092cab12a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F172827_69cdaa38d0369c5a78a5c7e092cab12a.png&h=40f3de54&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/172828_ec25941dd6a3e6d6395175977b2be557.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F172828_ec25941dd6a3e6d6395175977b2be557.png&h=7a47c1bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n士多啤梨的外型可愛，顏色又鮮艷，好受女仔既歡迎。不論是雪糕、蛋糕、甜品杯和飲品等都好常見到佢。我使用的這一種「女峰」甜中帶酸，加上蜜糖能補足甜味。"},{"pid":"da9fb7ccd687d253004322e35eac3978c6af08f4","tid":603991,"uid":17628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T09:32:04.000Z","msg":"賣相唔錯"},{"pid":"1d5db17a3bb5cfa5090d83f0dc5ff39b9accabd2","tid":603991,"uid":106919,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T09:35:05.000Z","msg":"<strong>手信篇</strong><br />\n<br />\n香港都有的大型日本連鎖超市中所購入的士多啤梨，真的十分甜，而且質地是實淨，很新鮮。只是400yen (28元)。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/173140_888b1edd1c70faf48524dea7aec6464f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F173140_888b1edd1c70faf48524dea7aec6464f.png&h=248f2ecc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/173143_704237f9c7e34df0c685fc13263763d9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F173143_704237f9c7e34df0c685fc13263763d9.png&h=2a273307&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n梨造型的梨啫喱。打開包裝，發現有一小匙和超可愛的小便箋說明這個小梨可以用來種花！有粒粒果肉，味道如一般的日式甜點偏甜。相信雪凍後味道更適中。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/173315_f31982b9c721b0617c4a535789593159.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F173315_f31982b9c721b0617c4a535789593159.png&h=98ada994&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/173316_ef691ff2f7902fbe139605c867a9a44a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F173316_ef691ff2f7902fbe139605c867a9a44a.png&h=d233dfe3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/173318_e64b1a24fe7799aed1e3a19cdac9af23.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F173318_e64b1a24fe7799aed1e3a19cdac9af23.png&h=23725016&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後是日本包裝的極致 - 首先有一個唔hea的不織布袋連一條唔hea的綿繩。入面是一份開二的小木籤，一份開二的梨蜜。真身是兩個小膠盒，載住三小塊「大風呂敷」黃豆粉團子。黃豆粉很香，質地幼細，是正宗日式風味。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/173454_a6edd2c830a8ad1122bdd73880a58193.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F173454_a6edd2c830a8ad1122bdd73880a58193.png&h=29f0f3ce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/173455_81b40344be68c7e2a69e8a70339a79d6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F173455_81b40344be68c7e2a69e8a70339a79d6.png&h=c42c0653&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/173457_5136685a16f6659be336df849d92d590.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F173457_5136685a16f6659be336df849d92d590.png&h=7992be9b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99a33546e5fad7e52b79b5b9e5cd33ae51f92cae","tid":603991,"uid":106919,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T09:51:14.000Z","msg":"Wordpress:<br />\n<a href=\"http://supermarketfantasyblog.wordpress.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsupermarketfantasyblog.wordpress.com&d=ZJyhSy%2F3CVi2leHjjJ8y7Yzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=940d4314\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">supermarketfantasyblog.wordpress.com</a><br />\nFacebook: supermarketfantasy 超級市場幻想<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Supermarketfantasy-超級市場幻想-1909246362631621/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSupermarketfantasy-%E8%B6%85%E7%B4%9A%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E5%B9%BB%E6%83%B3-1909246362631621%2F&d=ZJyhSy%2F3CVi2leHjjJ8y7Yzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=1ed5065f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Supermarketfantasy-超級市場幻想-1909246362631621/</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/smfsupermarketfantasy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fsmfsupermarketfantasy&d=ZJyhSy%2F3CVi2leHjjJ8y7Yzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=41b731bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/smfsupermarketfantasy</a>"},{"pid":"942b6956b76711992ac61535a32a872b78c12261","tid":603991,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T09:52:35.000Z","msg":"好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daa26e34604f8d82a72d508663b4cf